{"tid":2024404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"毛澤東屌鳩監警會報告","createTime":"2020-05-19T14:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T16:03:08.000Z","uid":38139,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d52fefa6f06f08810fa883d1e81dc61e5a1c89ed","tid":2024404,"uid":38139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:54:06.000Z","msg":"1930年5月毛澤東為了反對當時紅軍中存在的教條主義思想，專門寫了《反對本本主義》一文，提出<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;沒有調查，沒有發言權&rdquo;</span></span>的著名論斷。他指出：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;你對某個問題沒有調查，就停止你對某個問題的發言權。&rdquo;&ldquo;注重調查！&rdquo;&ldquo;反對瞎說！&rdquo;</span></span></strong>&ldquo;中國革命鬥爭的勝利（略）......到群眾中作實際調查去！&rdquo;這個論斷後來成為中國共產黨人深入實際，深入群眾，形成正確工作方法的行動口號。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">來源：中國共產黨新聞網</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://dangshi.people.com.cn/BIG5/221024/221027/14907173.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdangshi.people.com.cn%2FBIG5%2F221024%2F221027%2F14907173.html&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7gwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=9308ee67\" target=\"_blank\">http://dangshi.people.com.cn/BIG5/221024/221027/14907173.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jWyfqRk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjWyfqRk.png&h=cb1c04f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c0gpjct.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc0gpjct.png&h=f63f9add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好畀中共spin 走正史<br />\n可能你會以為吹大咗<br />\n但政府以後就用監警會報告<br />\n當<span style=\"color: red;\">正確歷史</span><br />\n消滅左我地香港呢班人<br />\n<br />\n往後歷史就無721警黑鉤結<br />\n只有黑白衣人互相毆打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb5d46d1c280932b383b1bfd378e68274e76cc9","tid":2024404,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"無主席好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1301df0f0440b3cc7125f7b452209f6ac61d95f5","tid":2024404,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:55:56.000Z","msg":"問心 大家想唔想香港獨立建國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024303</a><br />\n<br />\n我地抗爭要成功 首要改變返我地套mindset<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024244</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"613579f538452564fa98742d93aa72e1f948c8a2","tid":2024404,"uid":36901,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vOxUOgO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvOxUOgO.jpg&h=514feed8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d145c2563460156d0dde62bc6d2ff0f1291301fd","tid":2024404,"uid":38139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d89cce4aa921f47323ba429bd9c88e530328712","tid":2024404,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:04:18.000Z","msg":"毛主席有先見之明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373c39b51d052e0c7859056717a684f3caf127bd","tid":2024404,"uid":38139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T15:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a459d7d46787ae815d1e18c7c08994d541e3919","tid":2024404,"uid":38139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T16:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}